Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:45.26,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.01,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}I Can Tell When Someone's Lying
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.71,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I Can Tell When Someone's Lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.39,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell when someone's \Nlying, right, Raia?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:56.46,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can tell when someone's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:58.62,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,So if a liar said that they were a liar,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.90,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be able to figure \Nout if that's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.63,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can tell when someone's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.80,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if a liar is telling \Nyou that they're lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:13.04,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,they're just honestly telling you that \Nthey're lying, but it's hard to tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:16.69,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,But wait. Maybe they're \Nlying about being a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:21.71,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,But that would mean they're honest,\N and honest people don't lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:22.89,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,So that would make them a liar,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.88,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,but liars wouldn't just come out \Nand say that they're liars...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:32.64,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... uh... I... \NI don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:37.38,top,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... I don't know...\N I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:37.38,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,This is a famous paradox. All of \Nyou should think about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.03,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,That guy isn't Ronne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:45.31,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,This magic... Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:49.88,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NPage 115: "Mastermind."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 115\N\N{\fs18} Mastermind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:53.99,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... What have we been \Ntrying to do this whole time?
